  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div xml:id="KT55-kilavi">
          <p type="edition">nī varaivoṭu pukutāyēl ivaḷ iṟantu paṭum eṉat tōḻi talaimakaṉ ciṟaippuṟamākac (C3: ciṟaippuṟattāṉākac) colliyatu.</p>
          <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Uttered when HE was behind the hedge by the confidante, to say that she would die if he didn't come up with the marriage.</p>
          </div>



        <div xml:id="KT55">
            <lg type="edition">
<l>                mākkaḻi maṇippūk kūmpat tūttiraip</l>
<l>                poṅkupitirt tuvalaiyoṭu maṅku ṟaiik</l>
<l>                kaiyaṟa vanta taivara lūtaiyō</l>
<l>                ṭiṉṉā vuṟaiyuṭ ṭākuñ</l>
<l>                ciṉṉāṭ ṭammavic ciṟunal lūrē.</l>
             </lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
             <l>Alas, [just] a few days has this little good village,</l>
             <l rend="indent">[before] becoming an unpleasant abode</l>
             <l rend="indent">
                <choice>
                <seg>with abrasive cold wind, come for hands to part,</seg>
                <seg>with rubbing cold wind, come for [all] action to subside,</seg>
             </choice>
            </l>
            <l rend="indent">the clouds enmeshed with sprays of foam<note place="foot">The syntax of the lines 1-3, or rather the connection between the three joint elements <term xml:lang="ta">tirai</term>, "wave" – <term xml:lang="ta">maṅkul</term>, "cloud" and <term xml:lang="ta">ūtai</term>, "cold wind", is rather unclear. TVG understands <term xml:lang="ta">taii</term> (even more favourable to such an interpretation is the variant <term xml:lang="ta">taiiya</term>) as a link between <term xml:lang="ta">maṅkul</term> and <term xml:lang="ta">ūtai</term>, that is "wind tied to clouds with [rain]drops". The problem, then, is the connection to the preceding elements. He can only read "and foaming spray of clear waves".</note></l>
            <l rend="indent">from the pure waves, so that sapphire flowers close</l>
            <l rend="indent4">in the dark backwaters.</l>
             
                </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
